            function resizeImageAndGetBase64(img, maxWidth, maxHeight) {

                if (width > height) {

                    if (height > maxHeight) {

                canvas.width = width;

                const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');

            // --- Fun√ß√µes de Processamento de Imagem (n√£o alteradas) ---
            function rgbToHsv(r, g, b) {
                r /= 255; g /= 255; b /= 255;
                let h, s, v;
                const min = Math.min(r, g, b);
                const max = Math.max(r, g, b);
                v = max;
                const delta = max - min;
                if (delta === 0) { h = 0; }
                else if (max === r) { h = ((g - b) / delta) % 6; }
                else if (max === g) { h = (b - r) / delta + 2; }
                else { h = (r - g) / delta + 4; }
                h = Math.round(h * 60);
                if (h < 0) h += 360;
                s = max === 0 ? 0 : delta / max;
                return [h, s, v];
            }

            function createHistogram(imageData) {
                const bins = 8;
                const hist = new Array(bins * bins * bins).fill(0);
                for (let i = 0; i < imageData.length; i += 4) {
                    const [h, s, v] = rgbToHsv(imageData[i], imageData[i + 1], imageData[i + 2]);
                    const hBin = Math.floor(h / (360 / bins));
                    const sBin = Math.floor(s * (bins - 1));
                    const vBin = Math.floor(v * (bins - 1));
                    const index = hBin * bins * bins + sBin * bins + vBin;
                    hist[index]++;
                }
                return hist;
            }

            function calculateCorrelation(hist1, hist2) {
                let mean1 = hist1.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val, 0) / hist1.length;
                let mean2 = hist2.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val, 0) / hist2.length;
                let numerator = 0;
                let denominator1 = 0;
                let denominator2 = 0;
                for (let i = 0; i < hist1.length; i++) {
                    const diff1 = hist1[i] - mean1;
                    const diff2 = hist2[i] - mean2;
                    numerator += diff1 * diff2;
                    denominator1 += diff1 * diff1;
                    denominator2 += diff2 * diff2;
                }
                const denominator = Math.sqrt(denominator1) * Math.sqrt(denominator2);
                if (denominator === 0) return 0;
                return numerator / denominator;
            }

            populateModelDropdown();
        });

            // Nova fun√ß√£o para redimensionar a imagem e obter o Base64
            function resizeImageAndGetBase64(img, maxWidth, maxHeight) {
                const canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
                let width = img.width;
                let height = img.height;

                if (width > height) {
                    if (width > maxWidth) {
                        height *= maxWidth / width;
                        width = maxWidth;
                    }
                } else {
                    if (height > maxHeight) {
                        width *= maxHeight / height;
                        height = maxHeight;
                    }
                }
                
                canvas.width = width;
                canvas.height = height;
                
                const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
                ctx.drawImage(img, 0, 0, width, height);
                
                return canvas.toDataURL('image/jpeg', 0.8);
            }

            // --- Fun√ß√µes para Fotos Modelo ---
            function handleImageLoad(input, previewElement, callback) {
                const file = input.files[0];

                        img.onload = () => {

                                previewElement.src = e.target.result;
                                previewElement.classList.remove('hidden');

                            const resizedBase64 = resizeImageAndGetBase64(img, 500, 500);
                            callback(img, resizedBase64);
                        };
                        img.src = e.target.result;
                    };
                    reader.readAsDataURL(file);
                }
            }

            // --- Fun√ß√µes de Processamento de Imagem (n√£o alteradas) ---
            function rgbToHsv(r, g, b) {
                r /= 255; g /= 255; b /= 255;
                let h, s, v;
                const min = Math.min(r, g, b);
                const max = Math.max(r, g, b);
                v = max;
                const delta = max - min;
                if (delta === 0) { h = 0; }
                else if (max === r) { h = ((g - b) / delta) % 6; }
                else if (max === g) { h = (b - r) / delta + 2; }
                else { h = (r - g) / delta + 4; }
                h = Math.round(h * 60);
                if (h < 0) h += 360;
                s = max === 0 ? 0 : delta / max;
                return [h, s, v];
            }

            function createHistogram(imageData) {
                const bins = 8;
                const hist = new Array(bins * bins * bins).fill(0);
                for (let i = 0; i < imageData.length; i += 4) {
                    const [h, s, v] = rgbToHsv(imageData[i], imageData[i + 1], imageData[i + 2]);
                    const hBin = Math.floor(h / (360 / bins));
                    const sBin = Math.floor(s * (bins - 1));
                    const vBin = Math.floor(v * (bins - 1));
                    const index = hBin * bins * bins + sBin * bins + vBin;
                    hist[index]++;
                }
                return hist;
            }

            function calculateCorrelation(hist1, hist2) {
                let mean1 = hist1.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val, 0) / hist1.length;
                let mean2 = hist2.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val, 0) / hist2.length;
                let numerator = 0;
                let denominator1 = 0;
                let denominator2 = 0;
                for (let i = 0; i < hist1.length; i++) {
                    const diff1 = hist1[i] - mean1;
                    const diff2 = hist2[i] - mean2;
                    numerator += diff1 * diff2;
                    denominator1 += diff1 * diff1;
                    denominator2 += diff2 * diff2;
                }
                const denominator = Math.sqrt(denominator1) * Math.sqrt(denominator2);
                if (denominator === 0) return 0;
                return numerator / denominator;
            }
